prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon raccoon, looking slightly guilty and mischievous, is perched atop a giant, wobbly stack of brightly wrapped birthday presents. The raccoon is wearing a tiny, crooked party hat and holding a half-eaten slice of birthday cake. Below the illustration, in the center, is elegant, handwritten cursive script that reads: "I got you presents. I also ate your cake. Happy Birthday!" The entire design is a flat 2D watercolor painting, featuring soft, flowing colors, visible paper texture, artistic brush strokes, and organic paint bleeds at the edges of the figures.
